A remake of zm_hellarch...it has lots of secrets and invisible platforms and all locations have 2 or more ways to to it on map so it can't get unfair to zombies...I have also included bots(.nav file)

If i am missing anyone on the credits let me know and i will add you.

EDIT: As of 01/12/10 the map has been updated to allow 64 players and also has full VVIS compile settings and it still has bots as well
